Street Fighter II is the arcade fighting game that kicked off the "fighting game revolution" of the 1990s. Play as one of eight martial arts warriors as you travel the world to knock your opponents out of the tournament!
How long is Street Fighter II?
When focusing on the main objectives, Street Fighter II is about 1½ Hours in length. If you're a gamer that strives to see all aspects of the game, you are likely to spend around 11 Hours to obtain 100% completion.
